                        amp-img(src="img/content/partners/item_1.svg" layout="fixed" width="167" height="50")
                        p Tron is a blockchain-based decentralized platform that aims to build a free, global digital content entertainment system with distributed storage technology, and allows easy and cost-effective sharing of digital content.
                        p Tron was founded in September 2017 by a Singapore based non-profit organization called the Tron Foundation. It is headed by CEO Justin Sun and has a dedicated in-house development team that includes renowned technology stalwarts.
                        a(href="#!") www.tron.network

